Redesign the Achievements screen and the "Compare with me" screen completely.
The current screens are plain flat lists with no visual hierarchy, no achievement icons,
no unlock indicators, and no sense of progress. Replace them with premium dark gaming UI
using the existing gn_* design tokens.

