## Filter Row (below progress header)

Horizontal scrollable FilterChip row with three chips:
- "All"       — always shows all achievements
- "Unlocked"  — shows only earned achievements
- "Locked"    — shows only unearned achievements

Selected chip: gnAccentSubtle background, gnAccentGlow text
Unselected chip: gnBgElevated background, gnTextSecondary text
gnBorderCard stroke, 20dp corner radius

