DESIGN CONSTRAINTS (do not deviate)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

- Background: gnBgDeepest (#09090F) on all screens
- Cards: gnBgSurface (#12121C), 10-12dp corners, gnBorderCard 1dp stroke, elevation=0
- All text: GameNativeFontFamily (Outfit) via PluviaTypography
- Do NOT add new color values — only use existing gn_* tokens from Color.kt:
    gnBgDeepest, gnBgSurface, gnBgElevated, gnBgOverlay
    gnAccentPrimary, gnAccentGlow, gnAccentSubtle
    gnNeonTeal, gnNeonPurple, gnNeonOrange
    gnTextPrimary, gnTextSecondary, gnTextTertiary
    gnStatusInstalled, gnStatusDownloading, gnStatusError
    gnBorderCard, gnDivider
- No elevation shadows anywhere — use gnBorderCard stroke instead
- Unlocked achievement accent color = gnNeonTeal
- Your progress accent = gnAccentPrimary / gnAccentGlow gradient
- Friend progress = gnTextSecondary (neutral, not competing with your color)
- Achievement icon loading: use existing landscapist-coil pattern from LibraryAppItem
- Locked icon images: apply ColorMatrix desaturate + 0.35f alpha via Coil's ColorFilter
- List spacing: 8dp between cards in LazyColumn
- Horizontal padding on all screens: 16dp
- Section label style: 11sp, gnTextTertiary, uppercase, letterSpacing=0.10em
  (same as used in LibraryListPane section headers)
